{"tid":2436762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍店又得分 星光行美心潮庭48歲男侍應 發病發冷2日仍上班","createTime":"2021-03-07T11:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T12:00:02.000Z","uid":368777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2fdce6c61cafafe63185b29b043b0b2b11dde8c","tid":2436762,"uid":368777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"本港今日（7日）初步確診約8宗武漢肺炎，衞生署預告當中約5宗源頭不明個案詳情。其中中招的尖沙嘴星光行藍店美心潮庭48歲男侍應，3月4日發病發冷，5日去檢測，但4至6日仍上班，傳染期（發病前2日起計）或長達5日。<br />\n<br />\n潮庭侍應中招，被問到會否要求食客檢測，衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君就指，食肆的工作人員會檢視染疫侍應有多少緊密接觸者，若少量的話會送去檢疫中心，若有大量人士就要強制檢測，並要關閉食肆14日。張又提醒市民，在餐廳工作的人士要留意自己的身體狀況，有不適就應檢測，因為以往間中有餐廳爆疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/5PSTHKYKONDJ5BQ5ZTS66RCUNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GhKcyOpl1_6xUp4QbryTIbF4goMnknvlrHLx6NB5sAOkmfTNM_bRKnOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2F5PSTHKYKONDJ5BQ5ZTS66RCUNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GhKcyOpl1_6xUp4QbryTIbF4goMnknvlrHLx6NB5sAOkmfTNM_bRKnOo&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=0f295d75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2F5PSTHKYKONDJ5BQ5ZTS66RCUNQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2GhKcyOpl1_6xUp4QbryTIbF4goMnknvlrHLx6NB5sAOkmfTNM_bRKnOo&h=c9e6aad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/5PSTHKYKONDJ5BQ5ZTS66RCUNQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2GhKcyOpl1_6xUp4QbryTIbF4goMnknvlrHLx6NB5sAOkmfTNM_bRKnOo</a>"},{"pid":"08ad80875f7898c6306b515e20d2b9624d374c69","tid":2436762,"uid":368777,